article_id:2441,category_name:News,title_name:A Prize Showcase Is Coming Soon! [Addendum] ,image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630575600"></span>]</strong></span><br>There was an issue with 5★ adventurer Cecile&#39;s Munch on a Manachew skill description in this notice. The skill damage after skill change was listed incorrectly.<br><br>Incorrect: Damage: 115 &times; 1 hit<br><br>Correct: Damage: 115 &times; 10 hits<br><br>Note: This is only a display issue.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>A Prize Showcase starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630648800"></span>.&nbsp;</div><div>Appearance rates for featured adventurers will be boosted during this showcase!</div><div><br></div><div>When you summon on the Prize Showcase, you will get a prize in addition to the adventurer or dragon who appears. <span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Prizes will be sent to the No Limit tab of your goodie box.</span></div><div><br></div><div>There are six categories of prize: platinum prize, gold prize, silver prize, bronze prize, fifth prize, and sixth prize. When you perform a tenfold summon, the tenth prize is guaranteed to be either a platinum, gold, silver, or bronze prize. Note that unlike tenfold summons, using 10 single summon vouchers at once doesn&#39;t guarantee that the tenth prize will be a platinum, gold, silver, or bronze prize.</div><div><br></div><div>For a full list of prizes and their appearance rates, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu when the Prize Showcase is active, then see Prizes under Appearance Rates.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Cecile (wind/rapid-fire manacaster)</div><div>5★ Civilian Leif (light/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Prize Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1630648800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1631512799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the prizes below.</div><div><br></div><div>■Platinum Prize</div><div>If you receive a platinum prize, you will receive one of the following, based on their appearance rates.</div><div>・Sunlight Stone &times; 1</div><div>・Damascus Ingot &times; 1</div><div>・Adamantite Ingot &times; 1</div><div><br></div><div>■Gold Prize</div><div>If you receive a gold prize, you will receive one of the following, based on their appearance rates.</div><div>・Sunlight Ore &times; 3</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 2</div><div>・Golden Key &times; 2</div><div>・Twinkling Sand &times; 7</div><div><br></div><div>■Silver Prize</div><div>If you receive a silver prize, you will receive one of the following, based on their appearance rates.</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1</div><div>・Sunlight Ore &times; 1</div><div>・Twinkling Sand &times; 3</div><div>・Damascus Crystal &times; 2</div><div>・Moonlight Stone &times; 2</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament &times; 2</div><div>・High Windwyrm&#39;s Tail &times; 3</div><div>・High Lightwyrm&#39;s Tail &times; 3</div><div>・Windwyrm&#39;s Greatsphere &times; 5</div><div>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Greatsphere &times; 5</div><div>・Rainbow Orb &times; 3</div><div>・Tempest Orb &times; 5</div><div>・Resplendence Orb &times; 5</div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
