<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b067970c0dc4794d8ad1ad07f3bd61ae2.png"></span><span>Pledge of Justice II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user a unique force strike that deals<br>two hits, the second of which inflicts bleeding,<br>and increases damage dealt by this force strike<br>by 20%. The user will be immune to knockback<br>while charging this force strike as well as when<br>executing it.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c43a6915f92c8c57a2d124df899670c72.png"></span><span>Poison Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/83bd9c8302b087a508daec2a8fc9b2cf2.png"></span><span>Debuff Skill Time +20%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases duration of debuff skills by 20%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For a list of prizes and their appearance rates, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, and see Prizes under Appearance Rates.</div><div>3. If you obtain duplicate items from a tenfold summon or from using 10 single summon vouchers at once, the item quantities for each item will be combined when sent to the No Limit tab of your goodie box.</div><div>4. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase will be on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1630562400,update_time1630650666